{"tid":1381180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"留意返，港澳扮咁講即係支持黑社會","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:28:05.000Z","uid":39752,"like":103,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"95f0cd25bd8017bed7d831461dc881a3c69783cc","tid":1381180,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"支持特首施政 = 柒婆唔會落台<br />\n支持警方執法 = 字面解<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支持愛國愛黨人士 = 支持黑社會出嚟打人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>配合埋之前影到嘅證據，可以向全世界所有媒體煲大</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有國家資助黑社會襲擊香港市民</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，佢哋真係好驚聽到記者會嘅人理解成香港人搞港獨，提都唔敢提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解呢"},{"pid":"c9839a2510f15033bda074c683ed5d0b1bf6ceed","tid":1381180,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［重開 長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c93acde5a500161a3133995c6d6d052e40dfae5","tid":1381180,"uid":39752,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明由六月九號開始啲吹水打手就已經係咁話香港搞港獨<br />\n點解你港澳辦又咁驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a96024f463201737316f85aba59baf33f2b34c25","tid":1381180,"uid":39752,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:51:31.000Z","msg":"再講多一個解讀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>強調大家搞經濟放低紛爭，即係好撚驚你搞到經濟，例如罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5d63e9600db1d3e2de64932a